original: Lindgren, Per-Gösta Alvar, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 17/8/04 i Gbg av köpm. Otto L. o. Anna Christoffers-son. G. 43 m. tandl. Margit Holmgren. Barn: Hans f. 44, Jonas 46. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 26, tandl :kand. 28, tandläkare 30. Vik. i Karlskrona 31, praktik i Gbg sed. 31, skoltandl. i Säve sed. 32.
translated: Lindgren, Per-Gösta Alvar, dentist, Gothenburg, born on 17/8/04 in Gothenburg, son of merchant Otto L. and Anna Christofferson. Married in 1943 to dentist Margit Holmgren. Children: Hans, born in 1944, Jonas, born in 1946. Completed secondary school in Stockholm in 1926, earned a dental degree in 1928, became a dentist in 1930. Temporarily worked in Karlskrona in 1931, practiced in Gothenburg since 1931, and worked as a school dentist in Säve since 1932.
